data.description: Welcome to your new stunning home located at 4714 Briargate ct, Park City Kansas 67219. This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom home boasts just under 2300 sq/ft of comfortable living space. Upon entering, you will notice the fabulous main level, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, and tasteful LVP and wood flooring throughout.  The basement is perfect for entertainment and big family gatherings, with a spacious open plan and a wet bar to keep your guests engaged. The fenced-in yard and huge 3 car garage are perfect for enjoying the outdoors and offering ample space for storage.  Located in a very nice and family-friendly neighborhood in Park City, this home is perfect for families looking for a comfortable and serene environment.  Don't miss out on this amazing home! Call us today to schedule a viewing and experience the ultimate in relaxation and comfort!
